backupInterceptors - Variable in class io.lambdacube.aspecio.AspectDescription
The sorted list of interceptors that will replace the current interceptor if the chosen interceptor is unregistered.
Interceptors are chosen using by comparing their ServiceReference, so a higher service ranking is preferred, and in the case of equal service rankings a lower service id will be chosen.
